'''穆赫辛·法克里扎德·马哈巴迪'''（{{lang-fa|محسن فخری‌زاده مهابادی}}；{{bd|1958年||2020年|11月27日|catIdx=Fakhrizadeh}}）是[[伊朗|伊朗]]的[[核物理学|核物理学家]]以及[[伊朗国防和武装部队后勤部|伊朗國防部]]核計劃負責人、副部长<ref name="Guardian"/><ref>{{cite news |title=伊朗一核科学家遭遇暗杀身亡 系国防部核计划负责人 |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/11-28/9349426.shtml}}</ref>，具[[伊斯兰革命卫队|伊斯兰革命卫队]]-{准}-将军衔<ref>{{Cite web|title=Iran vows retaliation after top nuclear scientist shot dead near Tehran|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/27/mohsen-fakhrizadeh-iranian-nuclear-scientist-reportedly-shot-dead-near-tehran|accessdate=2020-11-29|date=2020-11-27|work=the Guardian|language=en}}</ref>。他也在位于德黑兰的[[伊玛目侯赛因大学|伊玛目侯赛因大学]]教授物理<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Secret Nuclear Dossier: Intelligence from Tehran Elevates Concern in the West - DER SPIEGEL - International|url=https://www.spiegel.de/international/world/the-secret-nuclear-dossier-intelligence-from-tehran-elevates-concern-in-the-west-a-673802.html|accessdate=2020-11-29|last=SPIEGEL|first=Holger Stark, Erich Follath, Dieter Bednarz, DER|work=www.spiegel.de|language=en}}</ref>。他建立并领导了{{le|伊朗防御性创新研究组织|Organization of Defensive Innovation and Research}}。他被任命为伊朗国防和武装部队后勤部的高级科学家，并担任[[拉维赞·什安物理研究中心|拉维赞·什安物理研究中心]]（PHRC）的负责人。他被认为是伊朗核武器项目的“灵魂人物”，有西方外交官曾称他为“伊朗核弹之父”<ref name="tg01">{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/27/mohsen-fakhrizadeh-iranian-nuclear-scientist-reportedly-shot-dead-near-tehran |title=Iran's top nuclear scientist shot dead near Tehran |publisher=The Guardian |date=2020-11-27}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=伊朗高级核物理学家遭暗杀身亡|url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20201128/20201128A01RFA00.html|accessdate=2020-11-28|author=观察者网 鞠峰|date=2020-11-28|format=|publisher=腾讯网|language=zh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128043835/https://new.qq.com/omn/20201128/20201128A01RFA00.html|archivedate=2020-11-28}}</ref>。

==生平==
法克里扎德於1958年出生於[[库姆|库姆]]，1987年于[[沙希德·贝赫什提大学|沙希德·贝赫什提大学]]获学士学位，之后在{{tsl|en|Isfahan University of Technology|伊斯法罕科技大学}}学习核放射与宇宙射线<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-12-01|title=Isfahan University of Technology boards massage of condolences on assassinaton of esteemed graduate of IUT, Dr.Mohsen Fakhrizadeh|url=https://news.iut.ac.ir/news/30525|access-date=1 December 2020|publisher=[[Isfahan_University_of_Technology|Isfahan University of Technology]]|language=fa}}</ref>，取得博士学位<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-11-28|title=Killing of suspected Iranian nuclear mastermind risks confrontation as Trump exits|url=https://www.irinn.ir/fa/news/805125/شهید-محسن-فخری-زاده-را-بیشتر-بشناسید|access-date=29 November 2020|publisher=[[Islamic_Republic_of_Iran_News_Network|Islamic Republic of Iran News Network]]|language=fa}}</ref>。在1979年[[霍梅尼|霍梅尼]]推翻国王[[穆罕默德-礼萨·巴列维|穆罕默德·礼萨·巴列维]]后加入了[[伊斯兰革命卫队|革命卫队]]，后获-{准}-将军衔。此外，他后来也担任伊朗國防部副部長及屬下防禦性創新研究組織負責人。1991年后担任[[伊玛目侯赛因大学|伊玛目侯赛因大学]]物理學教授<ref name="#1">{{Cite book|title=伊朗核计划的发展轨迹 |last=Gaietta, Michele|first=|publisher=帕尔格雷夫·麦克米伦（Palgrave Macmillan）出版公司|year=2015|isbn=978-1-349-57841-2|location=纽约：|pages=}}</ref>。

自2006－2007年起，法克里扎德受到[[联合国安全理事会|联合国安理会]]冻结资产和旅行通知的制裁<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sanctions Committee - 1737|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206092110/https://www.un.org/sc/committees/1737/desindv.shtml|accessdate=2020-11-29|date=2015-02-06|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>，理事会表示，[[国际原子能机构|国际原子能机构]]（IAEA）要求采访法克里扎德担任PHRC期间的活动，而伊朗拒绝配合。但伊朗提供了一些有关其工作的信息，国际原子能机构表示“与调查结果并不矛盾”，但将会寻求对其调查结果的佐证<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Iranian nuclear crisis : avoiding worst-case outcomes|url=http://archive.org/details/iraniannuclearcr0000fitz|publisher=Oxford : Routledge for the International Institute for Strategic Studies|date=2008|isbn=978-0-415-46654-7|last=Fitzpatrick|first=Mark}}</ref>。法赫里扎德在联合国2007年关于伊朗核计划的报告中被确定为“关键人物”<ref>{{Cite news|title=U.N. nuclear report puts Iran "mystery man" in spotlight|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-nuclear-iran-fakhrizadeh-idUSTRE7AA43J20111111|newspaper=Reuters|date=2011-11-11|accessdate=2020-11-29|language=en|first=Fredrik|last=Dahl}}</ref>。
[[File:Mohsen_Fakhrizadeh_1.jpg|thumb]]
在{{tsl|en|AMAD Project|AMAD项目}}终止后，法克里扎德建立并领导了国防创新研究组织（SPND），这是一个由政府资助的专门研究核武器的实体<ref>{{Cite web|title=Iran scientist linked to military nuclear program killed|url=https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/iran-scientist-linked-military-nuclear-program-killed-74427635|accessdate=2020-11-29|last=News|first=A. B. C.|work=ABC News|language=en}}</ref>，成立于2011年2月。其隶属于伊朗国防部和武装部队后勤部<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Rezaei|first1=Farhad|last2=Khodaei Moshirabad|first2=Somayeh|date=2018-03-15|title=The Revolutionary Guards: from spoiler to accepter of the nuclear agreement|journal=British Journal of Middle Eastern Studies|language=en|volume=45|issue=2|pages=138–155|doi=10.1080/13530194.2016.1214817|issn=1353-0194}}</ref>。

一份泄露给[[星期日泰晤士報|《星期日泰晤士报》]]的2007年伊朗内部文件确定，法克里扎德为扩大先进技术部署领域（FEDAT）的主席，该组织是运行伊朗核武器计划的组织的对外名称。这份题为《未来四年与中子有关的特殊活动的展望》的文件提出了开发铀氘化中子引发剂的四年计划<ref>{{Cite news|title=Leaked memo identifies man at head of Iran’s nuclear programme|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/leaked-memo-identifies-man-at-head-of-irans-nuclear-programme-s7pxjgztdkg|accessdate=2020-11-29|issn=0140-0460|language=en|first=Catherine Philp, Diplomatic|last=Correspondent}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Will Fereydoun Abbasi-Davani lead Iran to nuclear weapons? (Rev. 1) {{!}} Institute for Science and International Security|url=https://isis-online.org/isis-reports/detail/will-fereydoun-abbasi-davani-lead-iran-to-nuclear-weapons|accessdate=2020-11-29|last=Avag|first=Robert|work=isis-online.org|language=en}}</ref>。

=== 遇刺身亡 ===

[[File:Killing_of_Mohsen_Fakhrizadeh_13990907000542637421000496009615.jpg|thumb]]

2020年11月27日，[[伊朗国防和武装部队后勤部|伊朗國防部]]宣布法赫里扎德当日下午遇刺身亡<ref>{{Cite web|title=Eminent Scientist Fakhrizadeh Assassinated by Terrorists: Defence Ministry|url=http://irangov.ir/detail/352027|accessdate=2020-11-30|author=|date=2020-11-27|format=|publisher=GOVERNMENT OF THE ISLAMIC REPUBLIC OF IRAN|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130062045/http://irangov.ir/detail/352027|archivedate=2020-11-30}}</ref>，他是第五位被暗殺的伊朗科學家<ref>{{Cite web|title=Iranian scientist's death only the latest in long line of attacks blamed on Israel|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/27/iran-has-long-accused-israel-of-killing-its-nuclear-scientists|format=|publisher=THE GUARDIAN|language=en|archiveurl=|archivedate=}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Supreme National Security Council|伊朗最高国家安全委员会}}说，这起袭击未能防患于未然原因在于，“关于针对法赫里扎德刺杀的情报在频繁中使人对这些可能性放松了警惕，不幸的是，他们恰好在这次得手了”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Iran says nuclear scientist killed by remote-controlled device|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/30/iran-says-nuclear-scientist-killed-by-remote-controlled-device|format=|publisher=THE GUARDIAN|quote=On Monday, Shamkhani, the Iranian official, said there had been so many intelligence reports of a possible attack against Fakhrizadeh that an accurate prediction of Friday’s attack had been ignored.He said: “Due to the frequency of news during these 20 years, unfortunately, the required seriousness was not applied, and this time they succeeded.”|language=en|archiveurl=|archivedate=}}</ref>。法赫里扎德的儿子们指出，事发当日法赫里扎德已被情报部门警告可能遭遇暗杀的风险，但他还是出门前去参加一场会议<ref name="toi1">{{cite news|last=TOI Staff|date=5 December 2020|title=Fakhrizadeh's sons say he was shot 4-5 times, warned against travel before hit|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/fakhrizadehs-sons-say-he-was-shot-4-5-times-warned-against-travel-ahead-of-hit/|work=The Times of Israel|access-date=5 December 2020|archive-date=5 December 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205205138/https://www.timesofisrael.com/fakhrizadehs-sons-say-he-was-shot-4-5-times-warned-against-travel-ahead-of-hit/}}</ref>。

早期報導指出，案发时一辆装有炸药的货车在法赫里扎德所乘车辆附近爆炸，待车辆停驶后，又有殺手向其扫射<ref name=":0" />，受重伤的法赫里扎德被送医后抢救无效死亡<ref>{{Cite web|title=Iran vows retaliation after top nuclear scientist shot dead near Tehran|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/27/mohsen-fakhrizadeh-iranian-nuclear-scientist-reportedly-shot-dead-near-tehran|accessdate=2020-11-28|author=|date=2020-11-28|publisher=The Guardian|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128045008/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/27/mohsen-fakhrizadeh-iranian-nuclear-scientist-reportedly-shot-dead-near-tehran|archivedate=2020-11-28}}</ref>。目擊者表示有3至4名参与袭击的武装分子被殺<ref name="bbc01" />。但由於情況混亂，其後有其它報導描述了不同版本的刺殺過程<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20201130/00180_008.html |title=遇刺詳情曝光 12槍手拖出車處決伊朗核計劃之父 |work=東方日報 |date=2020-11-30}}</ref>。

事发两日后，伊朗所屬的[[法斯通訊社|法尔斯通讯社]]官方披露法克里扎德遭暗杀的细节内容，称现场无刺杀人员，乃是使用先進的遙控機槍進行刺殺。當時法克里扎德和他的妻子乘坐一輛[[防彈車|防彈車]]旅行，另有三輛安全人員的車與之隨行。突然有子彈擊中其中一輛車，法克里扎德下車查看。隨即在距離法克里扎德約150米處的一輛[[日產汽車|日產汽車]]裏的遥控操作的自动机枪向法赫里扎德射击，其中一发子弹命中其脊椎，在刺杀完成后搭载遥控机枪的日產汽車发生爆炸，伊朗情报部门调查发现车辆主人已于10月29日离境伊朗<ref>{{cite news |title=伊朗媒體：核科學家被遙控機關槍暗殺　至少被擊中3次 |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/555537/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94-%E6%A0%B8%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E8%A2%AB%E9%81%99%E6%8E%A7%E6%A9%9F%E9%97%9C%E6%A7%8D%E6%9A%97%E6%AE%BA-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD3%E6%AC%A1}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=جزئیاتی جدید از شیوه عملیات ترور شهید فخری‌زاده|url=https://www.farsnews.ir/news/13990909000920/%D8%AC%D8%B2%D8%A6%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA%DB%8C-%D8%AC%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%B4%DB%8C%D9%88%D9%87-%D8%B9%D9%85%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AA%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%B4%D9%87%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D9%81%D8%AE%D8%B1%DB%8C%E2%80%8C%D8%B2%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%87|accessdate=2020-11-30|author=|date=2020-11-29|format=|publisher=www.farsnews.ir|language=fa|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130063307/https://www.farsnews.ir/news/13990909000920/%D8%AC%D8%B2%D8%A6%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA%DB%8C-%D8%AC%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%B4%DB%8C%D9%88%D9%87-%D8%B9%D9%85%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AA%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%B4%D9%87%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D9%81%D8%AE%D8%B1%DB%8C%E2%80%8C%D8%B2%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%87|archivedate=2020-11-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3366333 |title=暗殺細節曝光！伊朗核武之父遭機槍遠端遙控射殺 無刺客在場 |work=自由時報電子報 |date=2020-11-30}}</ref>。伊朗政府一名消息人士表示，暗杀法赫里扎德的武器带有以色列军工产品的徽标，由以色列制造并由卫星控制<ref>{{cite news |title=伊媒：暗杀核科学家的武器带有以色列军工徽标，并由卫星控制 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/435560166_260616}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Supreme National Security Council|伊朗最高国家安全委员会}}秘书[[阿里·沙姆哈尼|沙姆哈尼]]在法赫扎里德的葬礼上表示，针对死者的刺杀行动经证实是一场复杂的远程刺杀行动，在现场并没有杀手参与其中<ref name=“t”> {{Cite web|title=伊朗证实法赫扎里德被电子设备远程暗杀|url= https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20201201-1105364 |accessdate=2020-12-01|author=陈惠璋|date=2020-12-01|format=|publisher=[[联合早报|联合早报]]网|language=zh|archiveurl=|archivedate=}}</ref>。伊斯兰革命卫队副总司令{{tsl|en|Ali Fadavi|阿里·法达维}}表示，袭击中使用的武器配备一个摄像头且利用了人工智能技术，通过[[人造卫星|人造卫星]]实现远程遥控，以此来精确定位作为刺杀目标的法赫里扎德。他并声明法赫里扎德始终停留在座驾上，150米处遥控机枪瞄准法赫里扎德，共射出13发子弹，其中4枪射向法赫里扎德的子弹被他的头号保镖挡下，但仍有造成致命伤的子弹射中他的脊椎，而坐在他旁边25厘米处的妻子却并未受伤（这点也受到他的儿子证实<ref name="toi1"/>）。随后，搭载机枪的日产品牌卡车自毁，整个过程持续约3分钟<ref>{{Cite web|title=Iran says nuclear scientist killed by remote-controlled device|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/30/iran-says-nuclear-scientist-killed-by-remote-controlled-device|format=|publisher=THE GUARDIAN|quote=|language=en|archiveurl=|archivedate=}}</ref><ref name="mehr">{{cite news|date=6 December 2020|title=Terrorists used AI to assassinate Martyr Fakhrizadeh|url=https://en.mehrnews.com/news/166841/Terrorists-used-AI-to-assassinate-Martyr-Fakhrizadeh|work=Mehr News Agency|access-date=6 December 2020}}</ref><ref name="cnn3">{{cite news|last1=Mazloumsaki|first1=Sara|last2=McLaughlin|first2=Eliott C.|date=30 November 2020|title=Assassinated Iranian nuclear scientist shot with remote-controlled machine gun, news agency says|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/29/middleeast/iran-mohsen-fakhrizadeh-remote-control-machine-gun/index.html|work=CNN|access-date=30 November 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201140603/https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/29/middleeast/iran-mohsen-fakhrizadeh-remote-control-machine-gun/index.html|archive-date=1 December 2020}}</ref>。

2021年9月，《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》披露此次[[摩薩德|摩薩德]]暗殺行動使用遙控機槍，以AI輔助去補償延遲、震動和車速。<ref>{{Cite web|website=奇客Solidot |title=核科学家是被 AI 辅助的遥控机枪杀死的 |url=https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=69003|access-date=2021-11-09|work=www.solidot.org}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Scientist and the A.I.-Assisted, Remote-Control Killing Machine|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/09/18/world/middleeast/iran-nuclear-fakhrizadeh-assassination-israel.html|author=Ronen Bergman and Farnaz Fassihi|date=2021-09-18|subscription=yes|publisher=The New York Times|language=en|archiveurl=|archivedate=}}</ref>

而对于此处可能出现的对[[人工智能|人工智能]]在杀戮方面的运用，[[制止杀手机器人运动|制止杀手机器人运动]]成员、[[计算机科学|计算机科学家]]{{tsl|en|Noel Sharkey|诺埃·沙基}}表达了他的担忧：“如果这种袭击的罪魁祸首，是一种有自主性，且能通过[[人脸识别|人脸识别]]进行锁定与刺杀的智能设备的话，那全球安全进程就已经走了很大的下坡路了。”<ref name="bbc9">{{cite news|date=7 December 2020|title=Mohsen Fakhrizadeh: 'Machine-gun with AI' used to kill Iran scientist|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-55214359|work=BBC|quote=Professor Noel Sharkey, a member of the Campaign Against Killer Robots, said the consequences of military forces having access to such weapons would have "unimaginable consequences"."If such devices were autonomous, using face-recognition to pinpoint and kill people, we would be on a downhill roll that would entirely disrupt global security," he said.|access-date=2020-12-08}}</ref>

=== 其它 ===

本世纪前十年间，法赫里扎德主导了名为生命科学研究中心（the Biological Study Centre）的项目，外界普遍相信这是物理学研发中心（the Physics Research Centre，PHRC）的后继版本，而该项目的研究主要是在[[拉维赞·什安物理研究中心|拉维赞·什安]]进行的<ref name="#1"/><ref name="Guardian">{{Cite news |title=Mohsen Fakhrizadeh: key figure in Iran's nuclear efforts who avoided limelight |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/27/mohsen-fakhrizadeh-thought-to-be-key-figure-in-irans-nuclear-efforts |access-date= 2020-11-27 |work=The Guardian |date=2020-11-27 |language=en}}</ref><ref name=bbc01>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-55105934|title=Mohsen Fakhrizadeh, Iran's top nuclear scientist, assassinated near Tehran|publisher=BBC|date=2020-11-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=“伊朗核弹之父”遇刺　掌舵核计划多年　曾被原子能机构点名 |url=https://www.dwnews.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83/60220583/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%A0%B8%E5%BC%B9%E4%B9%8B%E7%88%B6%E9%81%87%E5%88%BA%E6%8E%8C%E8%88%B5%E6%A0%B8%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E7%82%B9%E5%90%8D}}</ref>。据称，法赫里扎德在伊朗抗击[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病]][[2019冠状病毒病伊朗疫情|当地疫情]]期间担任了重要角色。伊朗驻联合国代表{{tsl|en|Majid Takht-Ravanchi|马吉德·塔赫特-拉万奇}}表示，法赫里扎德领导了伊朗第一批自产[[2019冠状病毒病检测|检测试剂]]的研发<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/27/world/middleeast/iran-nuclear-scientist-assassinated-mohsen-fakhrizadeh.html|title=Iran's Top Nuclear Scientist Killed in Ambush, State Media Say|first1=Farnaz|last1=Fassihi|first2=David E.|last2=Sanger|first3=Eric|last3=Schmitt|first4=Ronen|last4=Bergman|date=27 November 2020|work=The New York Times}}</ref><ref name="bbc4">{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-55118140|title=Mohsen Fakhrizadeh: What were the motives behind his killing?|date=28 November 2020|work=BBC News}}</ref>。伊朗国防部长{{tsl|en|Amir Hatami|阿米尔·哈塔米}}提及法赫里扎德在抗击冠状病毒作出的科学贡献时说：“……他为我国研发COVID-19疫苗作出了巨大贡献……生命科学研究中心已经完成了疫苗第一阶段的临床人体实验……将为广大人民带来巨大福祉”<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://parstoday.com/en/news/iran-i130017|title=Research center run by Fakhrizadeh produced first COVID-19 test kits for Iranians: Defense minister|date=28 November 2020|website=Pars Today}}</ref>。

2020年11月29日，德黑兰抗疫指挥中心（the Coronavirus Battle Headquarters of Tehran）负责人吊唁时说，法赫里扎德是一位杰出的科学家以及一位可敬的学者，并感谢他生前在科学[[研究|研究]]、[[科技|科技]]研发和[[医疗卫生产业|公共卫生]]方面所做的贡献<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2020/11/29/2399872/official-highlights-fakhrizadeh-s-help-in-covid-19-battle-vaccine-development|title=Official Highlights Fakhrizadeh's Help in COVID-19 Battle, Vaccine Development - Society/Culture news|website=Tasnim News Agency}}</ref>。

