有评论员指，法赫里扎德之死无疑会加剧该地区的紧张局势，并使得美国候任总统[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]面对的问题更加复杂化，为他地区外交政策的制定设置了障碍<ref name="lat">{{Cite news|date=2020-11-27|title=Gunned-down Iranian nuclear scientist was an Israeli target for years|url=https://www.latimes.com/world-nation/story/2020-11-27/iranian-nuclear-scientist-killed-near-tehran-state-media|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127235819/https://www.latimes.com/world-nation/story/2020-11-27/iranian-nuclear-scientist-killed-near-tehran-state-media|archive-date=27 November 2020|access-date=2020-11-27|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|language=en-US}}</ref>。该起事件的发生碰巧是在报导指美国总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|特朗普]]意欲攻击伊朗核设施却被幕僚劝阻而未能成行的两周以后<ref>{{cite news|last= |first= |date=16 November 2020|title=Trump Sought Options for Attacking Iran to Stop Its Growing Nuclear Program|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/16/us/politics/trump-iran-nuclear.html|work=The New York Times|access-date=29 November 2020}}</ref>。前[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]政府伊朗政策顾问{{tsl|en|Robert Malley|罗伯特·默里}}指，这起事件的时间点似乎就像是为了让拜登与伊朗谈判之路增加挫折。而重新加入特朗普政府退出的[[联合全面行动计划|伊核协议]]是拜登的竞选承诺之一。<ref name="reuters">{{Cite news|last=Hafezi|first=Parisa|date=2020-11-28|title=Killing of suspected Iranian nuclear mastermind risks confrontation as Trump exits|language=en|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/iran-nuclear-scientist-idUSKBN2871OW|access-date=2020-11-28|archive-date=28 November 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128050131/https://www.reuters.com/article/iran-nuclear-scientist-idUSKBN2871OW}}</ref> 另有评论指这起事件不会为美国伊朗政策的制定与执行造成太大阻碍，[[耶路撒冷邮报|耶路撒冷邮报]]的一位特约编辑质疑指，若拜登有意修复美伊关系，伊朗方面冷眼相待并不会得到实际利益，何况这起事件与他关乎甚微<ref name="Jerusalem post">{{cite news|last1=Keinon|first1=Herb|date=November 29, 2020|title=Fakhrizadeh assassination is about far more than Biden - analysis|work=The Jerusalem Post|url=https://m.jpost.com/us-elections/its-about-far-more-than-biden-analysis-650627|access-date=29 November 2020}}</ref>。同时伊朗政府也表明，不会因此破坏与拜登政府的谈判计划，尽管伊朗国内舆论的报复声浪十分高涨<ref>{{cite news|last1=|first1=|date=2020-12-01|title=核专家虽遇袭身亡 伊朗称不会破坏与拜登政府谈判|work=Post|url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/international/story20201201-1105179|publisher=联合早报|access-date=2020-12-02}}</ref>。

